I"æ<p>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/nginx/nginx.conf</code>:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>map_hash_bucket_size 256; 
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Edit site configuration:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>map $request_uri $new_uri {
    default "";
    /&lt;$OLD_URI1&gt; /&lt;$NEW_URI1&gt;;
    /&lt;$OLD_URI2&gt; /&lt;$NEW_URI2&gt;;
    /&lt;$OLD_URI3&gt; /&lt;$NEW_URI3&gt;;
    ...
}

server {
  ...

  if ($new_uri) {
    return 301 $new_uri;
  }

  ...
}
</code></pre></div></div>

